    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Alpine White. This example is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Differential. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained with a documented Vanos overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The exterior retains its original factory finish with no evidence of oxidation, while the interior leather remains supple with no bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and free of any VANOS rattle or subframe fatigue, this is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist.",
