    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional vehicle that presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied annually; there are absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, retaining that distinct new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, creasing, or fading. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by master technicians at the dealership, with a thick folder of records to prove it. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of fluid seepage or heat fatigue. The original alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread depth. This is a collector-grade example suited for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
